      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what does that have to do with \"Goblin Slayer\"? That seems pretty irrelevant to a legal contract. Can you just stick to the legal implications? I'm trying to figure out if there are any specific \"hidden\" risks or sneaky things in this wording that I should be worried about.",
